      • branch

        public Tip branch()
        Builds a new tip branching directly from the current tip. The tip created is owned by the same character and the associated edge has delay zero.
        Returns:
        a new tip owned by the same character.
        See Also:

      • branch

        public Tip branch(int maxDelay)
        Builds a new tip branching directly from the current tip. The tip created is owned by the same character.
        Parameters:

        a new tip owned by the same character.
